的，為什麼有這麼多？<br />\n<br />\n我們反省就明白了，有意無意時時刻刻障礙別人。今生宿世，今生有這個現象、有這種行為，過去生中肯定有，生生世世所造的業，麻煩就來了。 所以，要懺除業障。<br />\n<br />\n業障怎麼懺除？要擴大心量，要慈悲一切眾生，愛護一切眾生，真有成就一切眾生的心願，這個業障才能解開。自己要懂得怎麼修行，怎樣去彌補自己的過失。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/edWi5oI9uFg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FedWi5oI9uFg&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7BhXM9JohKQ1t0lxADMilzY%3D&h=9375ede1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/edWi5oI9uFg</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T04:22:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/09OxK50IFl0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F09OxK50IFl0&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7BhXM9JohKQ1t0lxADMilzY%3D&h=8867c1bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/09OxK50IFl0</a><br />\n<br />\n樓主又唔理我啦<br />\n又睇唔到啦<br />\n又上網查啦<br />\n又叫人打電話問啦"},{"pid":"2d7a50b8525cd84f0ba42bc2ea9f0e10a51234f6","tid":2261428,"uid":176687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d93c229ab5995098c93f2dedffe6b94b9faccb95","tid":2261428,"uid":347001,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"112d9065499f2c2f943668efaa9771d1c8f5347e","tid":2261428,"uid":304856,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T14:07:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T23:40:11.000Z","msg":"起心動念為他人 做家務都是行善 因為為的是家人<br />\n努力工作 起心動念是為了服務大眾 都是行善<br />\n起心動念是好的 事事都是行善<br />\n<br />\n善中之善是法佈施 正法流通 令多點人變番做善人<br />\n善中之至善是勸人念阿彌陀佛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T04:23:41.000Z","msg":"樓主是否魔波旬<br />\n<br />\n樓主是否曲解佛法<br />\n<br />\n樓主是否懂雙修但不肯教渡眾巴打"},{"pid":"b8b2492548483b88b6a6e4fdca895efbea2bb4aa","tid":2261428,"uid":176687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"93ba910b1e9e3f8662678e461b82584bfe737e56","tid":2261428,"uid":69866,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"112d9065499f2c2f943668efaa9771d1c8f5347e","tid":2261428,"uid":304856,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-1